Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That weapon has the power to destroy\Nthe balance of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)あの兵器は\N世界のバランスを崩し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and lead it down the path\Nof its own destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,崩壊へと導く力です｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートのように！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Bahamut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)ギュッとして｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)私は 神の国に行きたい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to go to the land of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the old lady back in my village\Nwould talk about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん｡ 確か 里のばあちゃんが\N昔 よく行ってたって｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)行こう ニーナの里へ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us go to your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(隊長)報告に参りました｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not yet ascertained the whereabouts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)脱獄したジャンヌ･ダルク➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the fugitives Jeanne D'Arc,\NFavaro Leone and Nina Drango.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:20.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファバロ･レオーネ\Nニーナ･ドランゴの行方は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだ つかめておりません｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been multiple eyewitness accounts.\NIt is the same regarding the mysterious child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:27.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多数 目撃情報のあった\N謎の子供に関しても同様です｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:30.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイザル･リドファルドを\N拷問にかけておりますが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We are interrogating Kaisar Lidfard harshly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but he has maintained his silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も吐きません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the Orleans Knight captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)さすがは\Nオルレアン騎士団の団長だな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひっ！\Nもう少し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you were not ready for your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕を上げてから来い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱獄犯は お前たちに任せる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-I will leave the fugitives to you.\N-Yes, My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余は エイボスに向かう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be heading to Eibos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same\NAnd lose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz there are lots of roads to go\NBut I realize it's the road that's getting rougher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna walk straight ahead\NI lose another dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are broken before they can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the way you think it\NWhat the yielding heart reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Future, hope\NDespair, insecurity It's all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As hard as I kick\NThe reality which is lying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To the person I was when I prepared for it all\NGo your way don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But Walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)うっ！\Nカチャ(鍵を掛ける音)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫コツ コツ…\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(兵士)面会だ 起きろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dias!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ディアス｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I'm a real jailbird now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牢獄生活が\Nすっかり 板に付いてしまった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)鉄格子を握るより\Nあなたには剣が似合いますよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,An iron sword would suit you more than these iron bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)騎士団はどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose not much can be expected\Nwhen their captain is imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,団長が捕まっていては\Nどうもこうもないか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ディアス➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dias, I leave the Orleans Knights in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オルレアン騎士団を頼む｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)あっ… 団長は あなたです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ様に会った｡\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)はっ… ジャンヌ様に？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの方は\N何も変わってはいなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Orleans Knights will rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オルレアン騎士団は必ず復活する｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ様と共に\Nよみがえらせるのだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne is our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:03.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました｡\Nジャンヌ様と私と➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The three of us will return the knights to glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたとで｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it! My house is right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:34.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこ あそこ！\N私の家は あそこだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お～い！ はははっ はははっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははっ 痛いって｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たっだいま～！\N(一同)ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひひひひっ｡\N(子供たち)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nina!\N-Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Hey, you mean Sis, not Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ニーナ｣じゃないでしょ｡\N(子供たち)ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nina! How have you been?\N-Nina's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ｡\Nニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おばちゃん！ ニーナ 帰って来たよ｡\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニャー\Nあっ ピヨピヨだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Peep-Peep! This is a mora-\Nit's name's Peep-Peep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この子 モーラのピヨピヨだよ｡\Nニャー ニャー ニャー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Peep-Peep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)なぜ ｢ピヨピヨ｣なのだ？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But it's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かんない｡\Nけど かわいいでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)おかえりなさい ニーナ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm home!\N-I'm so glad you're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただいま～｡\N(母)いらっしゃい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)あっ 私は…｡\N私の友達のジャンヌさんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my friend, Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what they're wearing\Nin the capital nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)王都では\Nそういう服が はやっているのね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかえり ニーナ！\Nただいま～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(女性)おかえり ニーナ｡\Nただいま！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(女性)おかえり ニーナ｡\Nただいま～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Welcome back, Nina!\N-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ おかえり｡\Nたっだいま～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌさん 早く～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,置いていきますよ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バシャン！(泉に飛び込む音)\Nバシャン！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただいま～ ばあちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里のばあちゃんです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our village elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Jeanne D'Arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ… ダルクです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:42.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,置物じゃないよ｡\Nうっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! You've gotten thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(族長)\Nニーナ おめ 細くなったな｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なじょした？\Nなんだかんだっす｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよか ばあちゃん\N友達のジャンヌさんが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my friend Jeanne is begging\Nto get to the land of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なじょしても\N神の国さ行きてぇって言ってんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know you've been there before, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん\N神の国さ行ったことあんべ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell us how you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き方 教えてくんりょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い ばあちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飲むか？ ん？\N(２人)いや… どうぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, thank you.\N-No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two thousand years ago,\Nthe gods and demons worked together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:43.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000年前\N神と悪魔は 力合わして➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to take down Bahamut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バハムートをやっつけたっきょ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I took the tired gods
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんとき\N力尽きた神々を背中に乗っけて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and carried them to their homeland on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の国まで連れて帰ってやったんは\Nわしなんじゃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でた！ また その話だぎゃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I love this story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを見ろ｡\N(２人)ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(族長)あれは\Nあんときの わしの雄姿だべ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I looked like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どや？ かっこいいやろ｡\Nほれぼれするど？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, right? I was a looker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There' s no way you could fit\Neveryone on your little back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この背中に乗れるわけねぇべ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Pshaw!\N-Oh, she's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう知らね｡\Nあっ 怒った｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)おい ニーナ｡\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしても\N神の国へ行きたいのです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go to the land of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I implore your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とぞ ご協力を｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん ばあちゃん｡\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)何とぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I implore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん｡\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)何とぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Granny!\N-I implore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん？\N(族長)ぐぅ～…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝ちゃった｡\Nあっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん\N寝たら起きないから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't wake her up once she falls asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日 また来よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:55.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うい～ ふぅ～｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは すばらしいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このお湯 すごいんだよ｡\Nケガも治るし 疲れも取れるの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It even has healing powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえねえ ジャンヌさん➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jeanne, is Mugaro's dad cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロちゃんのお父さんって\Nかっこいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he has to be.\NYou've got it down, Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいよね そりゃあ｡\Nやるなぁ ジャンヌさん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの方は\Nそういうものではないんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not view that gentleman in such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢あの方｣だって｡\Nうふふっ｡ エッチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That gentleman? You're so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恋とか 愛とか\Nそういったものとは違う｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What was between us was not romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But they say that children are the fruit of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:36.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ～？\Nでも 子供は 愛の結晶でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの方は 今も エルと私を\N見守ってくださっている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he is still watching over El and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが全てだ｡\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そなたは どうなのだ？\Nえっ 私？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慕っている男性は いないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a man captured your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いる…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 かっこいい男の人に近づくと\N竜になって暴れちゃうから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I transform into a dragon\Nwhen I get near a handsome man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never really been able\Nto get close to anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:08.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと そういう人と\N仲よくできなかったんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's the only one I've been able to dance with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも その人だけは\N一緒に踊ることができたの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt safe when I was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にいて すごく安心できて\N幸せな気持ちだった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が生まれてきたのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost felt like I was born to dance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人と踊るためだったんだって\N思えるくらい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)初恋なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:32.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうね… そうかもね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)それは すてきだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌさんの初恋は\Nどんなだったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your first love like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)私は… 分からないんだ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I received my divine revelation before I knew romance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恋を知る前に啓示を受け\N神のしもべとして戦場にいた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and charged into battle as a servant of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the gods' servants not allowed to love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神のしもべって 恋できないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will find happiness with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナは\Nその者と幸せになれるといいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:07.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね 私の好きな人➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is, the person I fell for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の大嫌いな人だったの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,turned out to be someone I hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have no idea what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\Nどうしていいか分からなくて｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごくいい人なのに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really a great guy,\Nbut he's done a lot of horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしいこと いっぱいしてて｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)それでも好きなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも嫌いになれない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't bring myself to hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)私の中にも\Nいろいろな顔の自分がいる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I too have many different faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:49.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ｡\Nニーナの好きな人が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not strange that the man you like\Nwould have contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相反する顔を持っていたとしても\N不思議はない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなの？\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)もし ニーナが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are able to embrace\Nthose contradictions too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その者の\N全ての顔を愛せるのなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then your love may be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その恋は 本物かもしれない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供たち)フゥ～！\N(子供)わ～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供たち)ぷはっ！\N(子供たち)ははっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！ あんたたち！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinnertime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)ご飯よ！\N(子供たち)は～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:47.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌさん 似合う～！\Nそうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne, that looks so good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:50.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(一同)イケてる イケてる！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっただきま～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can you stay, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)\Nニーナは いつまでいられるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking a trip to the land of the gods tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日 ちょっと\N神の国に行ってくる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Land of the gods? I'll go too!\N-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)神の国？ 俺も行く！\N(子供)俺も！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)俺も！\Nダメ｡ 簡単には行けないんだから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come! It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の国に何しに行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to the land of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-To go see Mugaro.\N-Mugaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロちゃんに会いに行く｡\Nムガロちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供たち)誰？ それ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロちゃんは\Nジャンヌさんの子供で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugaro is Jeanne's holy child,\Nand he's been separated from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き別れの聖なる子だよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)聖なる子？ 分かんない｡\N(子供)うん 俺は分かる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-I get it though.\N-Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)うそつけ！\N(子供)分かるもん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not lying!\N-Then who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)じゃあ 誰だよ？\N(子供)聖なる子は 聖なる子だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-The holy child is the holy child!\N-So who is that holy child, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)\Nだから 聖なる子って誰だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,眠れないの？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's water over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水なら そこに｡\Nすみません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったら 少し お話ししましょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a strange village, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)不思議な里でしょう ここは｡\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ええ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も最初は 衝撃的だったわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really overwhelmed at first too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 私は 竜族じゃないの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not dragonfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from a nearby village, and I married in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,麓の村の出身で 嫁いできたのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is a wonderful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナは とてもいい子ですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are pictures of the parents\Nof the children we take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)あれね\Nうちで預かってる子たちの➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご両親の絵よ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The village is poor,\Nso they are all out earning money for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この里も景気が悪くってねぇ…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなで出稼ぎに行ってるの｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Nina's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ニーナのお父さんも？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子の父親は 死んだわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to protect the village\Nfrom the fireball 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:29.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１０年前 あの火の玉から\N里を守ろうとして 逃げ遅れて…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Nina cause any trouble for you\Nturning into a dragon or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)あの子 突然 竜になって\N迷惑かけなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ 命を助けてもらいました｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? She's growing up, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:49.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ～｡\Nあの子も成長したのかしら｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since her father died,\Nwhenever she gets near a man like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子 お父さんが死んだ日から➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お父さんくらいの男の人に\N近づくと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:58.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜になって\N暴れるようになっちゃったの｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll turn into a dragon and go on a bit of a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つらい記憶を思い出すのを\N拒否するようにね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as if to avoid painful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)ありがと ジャンヌさん｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:13.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子と友達になってくれて\Nありがと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてください｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't. I am not a person\Nwho deserves to be thanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:18.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 感謝されていい人間では\Nありません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... I am the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私がニーナの…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)はっ｡\N大変だったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell from how attached she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子の懐き具合で分かるわ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが\Nニーナに優しくしてくれたこと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell how kind you've been to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:40.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから ありがと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(母)つらかったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been through so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ううぅ～！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううぅ～…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ぶえぇ～！\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)｢あららら…｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ごほっ ごほっ…｡\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)だから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:15.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうやめなって言ったのに～｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ごほっ ごほっ ごほっ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:18.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケル子 こ… こんなときは\Nあれを言ってくれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cerby, I need you to say it again for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)ええ～？\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)早く言え！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)あんたが団長…｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)もっと大きく！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Louder!\N-You're the captain now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:27.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)あんたが団長！\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)よ～し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前を 団長の嫁にしてやるぞ！\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)ええ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you the captain's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)しっかりしろよ 団長｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ごほっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)やはり ここだったか｡\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:43.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nううっ はぁ…｡ おっ 副団長！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey there, Vice Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちわ～っす！ はははっ｡\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\Nオルレアン騎士団の騎士だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an Orleans Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じょ… 冗談じゃないですか｡\N何 本気で怒ってんすか？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting mad for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと ケ… ケル子～！\N(ｹﾙﾍﾞﾛｽ)まいど｡ ｢バイバ～イ｣｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cerby!\N-Please come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get enough sleep? I sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(族長)\Nお前たち よく寝れたべか？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは よく寝た｡\Nでしょうね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:14.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(族長)\Nお前たち 本気で行く気だべか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two serious about going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)お願いします｡\Nお願いします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…｡ うん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イエ～ス！\Nふぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で どうやって行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:30.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから わしの背中に\N乗せてやると言ったべさ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! I'll carry you on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:33.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ～？ だって その背中…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But your back won't-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ドドォーン！\Nうわ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごほっ ごほっ ごほっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm off, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さん 行ってくるね！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 行ってらっしゃい｡\N≪(子供)ニーナ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おみやべ 待ってる｡\N天使 連れて 帰って来る｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring back souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring home an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供たち)わあ～！\N(子供)やった～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)やったね！\N(母)ジャンヌさん➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of Nina for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナをよろしく｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってくるね～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nina! Bye!\N-Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供たち)ニーナ ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)気をつけて！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you protect Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌさんを\Nしっかり守るんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As horrible as you are\NI can't help but love you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while I waited\NThat is all I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ephemeral lovers, both flawed and missing pieces\NWe have finally become one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In this miniature garden at the edge of sorrow\NCan you hear my heart speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I may no longer feel\NThat I want to go back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are feelings I have that I only feel now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to escape with you Dancing\NJust like a fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it will only be this once, Darling\NI am on the same ark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shararanla Shararanla\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shararanla Shararanla\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shararanla Shararanla\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shararanla Shararanla\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:37.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと どのくらいもつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will it hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We exceeded the limits long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界は とうに過ぎています｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne!\NWhat can you cook best?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why all of a sudden? Cook best?\N- Uh ye- yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Rage of Bahamut:\NVirgin Soul, "City of the Gods: Part 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cook best...?\N- What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Soup made into stew!\N- That's just soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,BAHA SOUL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Baha Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to watch next time.
